name: Sagittarius Aiolos
description:
The savior of the infanta Athena and made a martyr by protecting her at the cost of his life. 
Later resurrected by Athena, to lay down his life alongside the other eleven Golden Saints in the destruction of the Wailing Wall in Giudecca. 
Despite being dead, some of his residual energy continues in his Cloth of Sagittarius and the House of Sagittarius.

#057 Saint Seiya Pack
